---
title: "Contrastive View Design Strategies to Enhance Robustness to Domain Shifts in Downstream Object Detection"
collection: publications
permalink: /publication/2023-robustviews
date: 2023
venue: '2023 AAAI Workshop on Practical Deep Learning in the Wild (Practical-DL)'
paperurl: 'https://arxiv.org/abs/2212.04613'
---

We propose strategies to improve the out-of-domain robustness of contrastively pretrained object detectors. In particular, we augment contrastive views to learn representations that are more robust to appearance-based and out-of-context domain shifts.   

